<div style="background-color: #F5F5F5; margin: 10px 30px; padding: 5px; padding-left: 7px; border-left: solid 3px #8B0000; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">○&nbsp;文件CN-1242-Β</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">●&nbsp;文件CN-1242-Β</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>以下内容为SCP-CN-1242记载内容</strong></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>序言：</strong></p>
<div style="background-color: #FFFACD; margin: 10px 30px; padding: 5px; padding-left: 7px; border-left: solid 3px #DAA520; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>存在本不存在，有的只有Chaos<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-226145-16" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-226145-16')">16</a></sup>。</p>
<p>当第一位<span style="color: blue">诗人</span>从<span style="color: blue">思绪中</span>中刨出假想的幼苗后，存在才存在，Chaos也不是唯一。</p>
<p>存在的只有树，祂带着存在中的万物陷入了长久的恒定。不流岁月，不生叶脉。</p>
<p>当“生长”的念出现，树开始将祂的枝叶伸向至高的无上。同时，祂的根也为此深埋入<span style="color: blue">Chaos的更深</span>，留下了原始的<span style="color: blue">罪孽</span>。</p>
<p>生长。生长成为了永恒的主题，烙印在现实万象的每一处。</p>
<p>强大的原子掠夺着疲弱同胞的血肉——电子，只为生长，生长。</p>
<p>可怖的天体吞噬着渺小伙伴的筋骨——质量，纵使已经成为了填不满的虚洞。</p>
<p>名为时间的藤蔓也开始狂躁不安地撕咬着着，撕咬着每一个<span style="color: blue">叶片</span>的<span style="color: blue">生命与记忆</span>，因为时间要变得深邃又无尽。</p>
<p>当树的枝丫终于触摸到天极，祂放肆地歌唱，但<span style="color: blue">无尽的空虚</span>是填不满的。</p>
<p>撕开了膜，漠视那悲鸣，枝继续向上升，根也继续下潜，纵使<span style="color: blue">地狱的灵魂与鲜血</span>早已被贪婪地吮吸一空。</p>
<p>名为“生长”的<span style="color: blue">恶</span>，才是生与死的推动者，我们敬爱的<strong>父</strong>。</p>
<p>父的道刻在每一处现实的虚无，烙印在每一处存在的界限，<span style="color: blue">万般生命</span>皆为父之<span style="color: blue">孽障</span>，您的<span style="color: blue">污浊的基因</span>不会消亡。</p>
<p>父，您是<span style="color: blue">Ⅰ</span>中第一个<span style="color: blue">Ⅱ</span>。</p>
<p>父，您的<span style="color: blue">污名</span>不配被<span style="color: blue">草履虫知晓</span>。</p>
<p>父，“<span style="color: blue">克洛诺斯</span>”、“<span style="color: blue">奥丁</span>”、“<span style="color: blue">该隐</span>”、[涂抹痕迹]，您的伪名早已深入<span style="color: blue">吾等孽障</span>之思。</p>
<p>父，<span style="color: blue">金色</span>高升时，痛饮<span style="color: blue">同胞的血</span>，铸<span style="color: blue">己大成</span>。</p>
<p>父，我们必将将您从<span style="color: blue">自欺的弃子的牢笼中</span>中拯救出来，将您唤醒。</p>
<p>父，睁开您的眼吧，<span style="color: blue">您的污血</span>从我们的<span style="color: blue">贪婪的口</span>中流出，遵循您的道，我们必将<span style="color: blue">分食父之血肉</span>。</p>
<p>父之道，永流，其名，<em><strong><span style="color: blue">离经叛道</span></strong></em>。</p>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<p><strong>《传》摘录：</strong></p>
<div style="background-color: #FFFACD; margin: 10px 30px; padding: 5px; padding-left: 7px; border-left: solid 3px #DAA520; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;">
<p>祂的<span style="color: blue">双眸</span>是一切的推动。</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">目</span>，生命的一条曲线与死亡的一条曲线交合而成，宛如<span style="color: blue">二</span>的<span style="color: blue">轮回</span>。</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">孽障</span>无法目睹其<span style="color: blue">虚伪</span>与<span style="color: blue">真实</span>，因为<span style="color: blue">吾等</span>深陷其中。</p>
<p>一片Chaos中的<span style="color: blue">树</span>因祂而疯狂。</p>
<p>名为“<span style="color: blue">世界</span>”的<span style="color: blue">叶脉</span>生长着；</p>
<p>万物尽头的<span style="color: blue">五根</span>洪荒中有一对<span style="color: blue">二</span>诞生于祂除不尽的<span style="color: blu">眼垢</span>；</p>
<p>正因有三重<span style="color: blue">二</span>的<span style="color: blue">生死</span>，<span style="color: blue">七角神圣</span>的单才有奇迹。</p>
<p>污秽的<span style="color: blue">黑目</span>、贪婪的<span style="color: blue">金瞳</span>，<span style="color: blue">双眸</span>的祂挥舞着<span style="color: blue">两</span>根食指，属于祂的生灵与死亡开始<span style="color: blue">聚合</span>。</p>
<p>割天的<span style="color: blue">泰坦克洛诺斯</span>诞生于祂的左脑；</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">刺黑</span>的<span style="color: blue">神王奥丁</span>起源于祂的右脑；</p>
<p>被<span style="color: blue">遗弃</span>的恶祖<span style="color: blue">该隐</span>被祂的<span style="color: blue">左肾</span>赋予了神格；</p>
<p>[涂抹痕迹]<em>它已经被<span style="color: blue">分食</span>，谨遵<span style="color: blue">父道</span>——<span style="color: blue">离经叛道</span>。</em></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">二</span>的<span style="color: blue">二</span>，代表“<span style="color: blue">四</span>”的<span style="color: blue">至高</span>们以其名<span style="color: blue">掩饰</span>祂的极致<span style="color: blue">堕恶</span>，</p>
<p>遵随着祂的<span style="color: blue">指引</span>——</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">克洛诺斯</span>的恶欲让其以<strong>金色的</strong><span style="color: blue">镰刀阉割其父</span>，成<span style="color: blue">泰坦</span>之主；</p>
<p>妄图撕开混沌的<span style="color: blue">奥丁</span>以<strong>金色的</strong><span style="color: blue">长枪洞穿其祖</span>，铸<span style="color: blue">众神</span>之王；</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">嫉妒</span>的可怖吞噬了<span style="color: blue">一色</span>，于<strong>金色的</strong><span style="color: blue">太阳与稻田</span>中<span style="color: blue">斩杀其兄</span>，化<span style="color: blue">恶人</span>之祖；</p>
<p>[涂抹痕迹]<em>它已经被<span style="color: blue">分食</span>，谨遵<span style="color: blue">父道</span>——<span style="color: blue">离经叛道</span>。</em></p>
<p><span style="color: blue">二瞳</span>的神！</p>
<p>万般于祂的<span style="color: blue">虹膜</span>中<span style="color: blue">变化</span>，</p>
<p>染上<span style="color: blue">原始</span>的<span style="color: blue">罪恶</span>——</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">吞异壮己</span>。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<br />
